data.name: Incoming data traffic from vehicle device
data.description: It is a data which includes informations like amount of fuel, current location of vehicle using network connection via satellite or 4g/5g communication and it is in process to be analyzed and security checked till reaching data centre

labels: Incoming data traffic from vehicle device

data.name: incoming filtered traffic
data.description: it is filtered data, which should be secured using security tools like firewalls, access controls ( user identification), encryption modules (checking security signatures)

data.name: Outgoing traffic from data center
data.description: data traffic which is processed and analyzed through Analytical engine process

data.name: unfiltered outgoing traffic
data.description: it is data which is being transfered to security check before reaching the client, and it is also analyzed information or service which is needed to be used for vehicle navigation

data.name: Outgoing traffic
data.description: It is a data which is going to be processed in Analytical engine

data.name: Incoming traffic
data.description: It is analyzed data coming from Analytical engine

data.name: Trust Boundary
data.description: communication between security and data store

data.name: Data Store
data.description: Some data will be checked like time, amount of fuel, user experience and duplicate information will be send to Analytical engine to be checked, analyzed and given response or result for client

threats.title: Overload
threats.description: A DDoS attack could overwhelm the data center, disrupting critical services like real-time tracking and telemetry analysis
threats.mitigation: Deploy DDoS mitigation services and load balancers to distribute traffic across multiple servers

data.name: Analytical engine
data.description: It is a process and analyzer which uses informations like navigation, vehicle performance, weather, driver feedback and personal data

data.name: Vehicle performance data
data.description: stores a handful of relevant information which is used by system to provide real-time information for the user

data.name: Navigation data
data.description: Provides routes and map data in order to to enhance the route planning and tracking systems

data.name: Weather data
data.description: stores real-time information of the weather which is useful for route planning and safety users

data.name: Driver feedback
data.description: contains feedback from drivers registered on the system which is then used to improve or fix any issues within of the mobile application

data.name: Personal data
data.description: It contains confidential information like user`s health condition, age, home address, bank details and personal activities and interests
